data.description: Imagine enjoying your coffee on a crisp cool Indiana morning or an evening sunset on the front porch swing. This is your chance to make it a reality in this wonderfully updated 2 story home in a peaceful country setting with mature trees and over an acre. Offering 4 bedrooms and over 2000 sq ft of living space this is one you don't want to miss! Give us a call today to set up your private showing.
